Jo and Peter Fancourt are seeing red – a lot of red – as they celebrate their ruby wedding anniversary with an extraordinary road trip across the UK.

To mark the momentous occasion, the Jersey couple is touring 40 places with ‘red’ in their names.

Redcar on Teesside and Redesdale in Northumberland are two of the stops on their 3,000-mile journey in a car covered in red ribbons.

