Before embarking on the road trip, the couple celebrated their anniversary with a trip to the Red River in northern Vietnam.

It is not the first time the couple has gone on an unusual adventure.

They have been house-swapping in the US and hostelling around Japan, and they have travelled by train to Siberia and Outer Mongolia.

